---
title: Thai Chili–Glazed Chicken & Sweet Potatoes Elevated Dinners, Impressively Easy
description: Our chefs are always working on ways to get you dinner faster, fresher, and tastier all the time. This addition to our Fast & Fresh lineup delivers seared chicken cutlets with a spicy-sweet chili glaze. On the side are buttery sweet potatoes sprinkled with crunchy sesame seeds and a colorful salad of mixed greens coated in a nutty sesame dressing with crisp sugar snap peas and sweet shredded carrots. Another sprinkle of sesame seeds and just like that, you’ve got another 15-minute winner dinner on your hands.
